normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-size-adjust: auto;\" /></span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Cleric Spells </span></strong>1st: @Item[Charm], 3rd: @Item[Enthrall], 6th: @Item[Mislead]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}
