efending during exploration without needing to move at half your travel speed, and you can perform another exploration activity as well. While you are using a shield, its Hardness increases by 5.<br><strong>Minor Curse</strong>: Shoddy artisanship makes itself known. Whenever an item youre using takes damage, it is broken.<br><strong>Moderate Curse</strong>: You must prove your skills at a craft by providing your own equipment. You gain item bonuses only from items you make yourself.<br><strong>Major Curse</strong>: You are forever cast out from your home. Members of your community have their attitudes towards you shift two steps worse, meaning those who used to be helpful are now indifferent, those who were friendly are now unfriendly, and all others are now hostile. This doesnt necessarily result in violence, but hostile community members generally seek your permanent exile.</span></p>"}
